name: Firebasenative
body:
### Welcome to FirebaseNative
FirebaseNative is a Unity plugin for extending the power of Googleâ€™s new Firebase toolset for your unity game. It provides unified cross-platform API for easy handling Firebase Notification and Firebase Analytics. It currently supports Android and iOS

### Features
* Obtain Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM) Token.
* Auto renew FCM token.
* Full Firebase Analytics support.
